11 minutes ago, Potato3478 said:

Ok srsly pls Halp

There are a bazillion ways this could've gone wrong, only log files and a screenshot of your GameData folder can provide the info we need. Simply "my game crashes please help" provides no info at all other than the fact that things are not working as intended.

@Potato3478 no idea what the error is, looking at that logfile. (Probably because it seems like computer gibberish to me)

Try the following: de-install Kerbol Origins and install only Kopernicus, ModularFlightIntegrator and ModuleManager. Check if the game runs, this way we can exclude either KO or Kopernicus as the cause of the problem.
Ok
Alright Kopernicus runs just fine
